      "details": "Created src/tools/ module as single source of truth for all tool implementations. Both the Ollama agentic tool-calling loop and the CPU SkillRegistry now delegate to crate::tools::execute(). Added 9 tools: read_log (with path-traversal guard), write_note, read_note, list_notes, send_email (outbox log), system_status, list_tools, get_beliefs, set_belief (both persist to beliefs.json). call_ollama_tools now publishes tool_call bus events to web_interface so the UI shows tool invocations with a distinct gold style. Slash commands (/status /tools /notes /beliefs /note /set /log /help) handled directly in web_server without going through LLM. CPU handle_bus_message now records user messages and bot replies in working memory. SkillRegistry registers all 9 tools + noop. dotenvy loads .env at startup.",
